This is a fork of cntext (https://github.com/hiDaDeng/cntext) originally
created by DaDeng and Peng Nan at Harbin Institute of Technology.

This fork has been adapted for English text analysis while maintaining the
original project's MIT License and preserving attribution to the original
authors.

